3. 지면이나 벤치에 힘을 전달하며 밀어 올리고, 마무리에서도 어깨 위치를 무너지지 않게 유지합니다.',
  description_en = 'Overview
Incline Dumbbell Press is a pressing exercise for the chest, front delts, and triceps. It is a key pattern for developing upper-body strength, pressing mechanics, and front-side muscular development.

Why do this exercise?
A strong press supports hypertrophy of the chest, shoulders, and triceps while also improving performance in many other upper-body training movements.

How to do it
1. Create a stable shoulder position and line up the wrists, elbows, and pressing path.
2. Control the lowering phase without losing tension or bouncing out of the bottom.
3. Press smoothly while keeping the shoulders organized and the torso stable.'
WHERE name_ko = '인클라인 덤벨 프레스' AND is_custom = false;

